Save gene names

gene_names <- rownames(scrna_sce)
gene_names[rownames(scrna_sce) %in% names(hg38_genes)] <- hg38_genes[rownames(scrna_sce) %in% names(hg38_genes)]$gene_name
rowData(scrna_sce)[["gene_name"]] <- gene_names
